{"tid":2132843,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[劭勸行動 Day 11] 停止搵手足參選，全面關注被DQ手足既後續安排","createTime":"2020-07-30T15:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T15:25:22.000Z","uid":266908,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fb63f0e49836b606fd6cda603e9c8403d20b3b83","tid":2132843,"uid":266908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:24:01.000Z","msg":"因應時間關係<br />\n本行動決定即時停止劭勸手足參選未有黃營代表參選之功能界別<br />\n<br />\n請大家轉為關注參選直選/功能組別後，被DQ之參選人所作出的後續安排，於必要時成為地區直選提名人，送作為Plan B / C 的手足入閘。只要你今屆選舉未提名過任何人又住喺當區，就做得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦請大家繼續幫以下差少少票就入到閘既手足，劭勸合資格既手足提名佢地<br />\n<br />\n保險界李福納先生：<br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/LeeFaulknerFIA/?__tn__=CH-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FLeeFaulknerFIA%2F%3F__tn__%3DCH-R&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDStUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=33b6670f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/LeeFaulknerFIA/?__tn__=CH-R</a><br />\n<br />\n商界 (第一) 手足 (仲未肯開名，請聯絡相關組群) ： <br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/businessvoters\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbusinessvoters&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDStUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=3981bd73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/businessvoters</a><br />\n<br />\n齊上齊落！不離不棄！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ca88360b20e1fbac8584d62bda96fcfcc347a7","tid":2132843,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:28:21.000Z","msg":"今日你開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42e464f547305e1af5ed70ef989b2a92177